This product embeds the BIP39 English wordlist (internal/builtin/english.txt),
sourced from the Bitcoin BIPs repository (bitcoin/bips, bip-0039). The wordlist
is used to encode the challenge/response phrases.

Third-party Go dependencies and their licenses are declared in go.mod / go.sum
(notably golang.org/x/crypto and golang.org/x/term, BSD-3-Clause).
